rows.label: tlk43300046_01_msg0002
rows.name:
That means I wash dishes,
peel vegetables, that sorta thing.

rows.label: tlk43300046_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Yeah, yeah. I know, OK?
I'm only just starting out.

rows.label: tlk43300046_01_msg0004
rows.name: I was a mercenary till right recently.

rows.label: tlk43300046_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I'd always launch the enemy in the air,
then smash them into the ground for
massive damage. I loved that combo.

rows.label: tlk43300046_01_msg0006
rows.name:
...Ah, but now, my biggest dream is
to become a cook at the court.

rows.label: tlk43300046_01_msg0007
rows.name:
I like to imagine Queen Lagert
one day eating the food that I made!
But for now I gotta keep peeling.
